# forges/ is now tracked as part of taf. Concrete forge instances live
# under forges/<product>/. Exclude runtime telemetry, local-only settings,
# and OS junk.
**/.entire/
**/settings.local.json
**/.phase-state.json
**/.session-token-log.jsonl
**/.last-sync
.DS_Store

# --- Phase 0 tourniquet (2026-05-17) ---
# Forge product-private overlay artifacts. Authoritative location is
# ~/workspaces/ta-set/private/forges/<product>/ (see PRIVATE.md per forge).
# Tools resolve via profile.yaml#private_root in Phase 1B.
forges/*/memory/
forges/*/.claude/holds.yaml
forges/*/profile.local.yaml
forges/*/.claude/resolve/contracts/C-*.yaml
